{"type": "article", "id": 61850, "title": "肯德基在成都开“博物馆”餐厅，Buzzfeed 制作了纸质报纸 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2019-03-07T05:55:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 4099, "name": "报纸"}, {"id": 616, "name": "博物馆"}, {"id": 199, "name": "Google"}, {"id": 114, "name": "Buzzfeed"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 54, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190307140731rp7kQ6W19lsSAwCd.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/1897368887/4346769267964779\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>VERO MODA 昨天宣布江疏影成为品牌形象代言人，</strong></a>她还出演了品牌 TVC 传递每位女性都是独特存在的观点。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307131030eTnqAOl24RK0QzZu.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.893849\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p> <a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5OTM4NTYyNA==&amp;mid=2653826860&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=f023d5bb90c0fe07c43c4fd6d8d9896b&amp;chksm=bce6c05b8b91494d29bc50d9f26b18f2324a2ef2fbd0ea11de006992c838f2346ee3dec00678&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=03079XXp1B3rFnQ5uATOQpJF&amp;key=483299f3b4f7cf0acf0f3ab69e8fd6812173e37e1c1c4719d165291376f39d12b9a40962780bd042c2cf885b68addb04d76f9e40ff9b1a6f50763c221fbca5d155c9f5cb769463d8e5eefc6327e1bca5&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14.3+build(18D109)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=QpTLgi65PvjLiRvj%2BrHXN3H8SOsbAbhr3zv40fOynI6ec%2BFFK6jRa0dX6BwFHY2L\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Diesel 发布了主题为“敢活敢怂”的品牌广告片。</strong></a>片中分别选择了派对、洗衣和旅行三个场景，倡导遵从“内心”的选择，不要“怂”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=o0845anv41x\"></iframe> </figure> </div><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=a0845w6ndvq\"></iframe> </figure> </div><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=w0845myfk2c\"></iframe> </figure> </div><p><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4346739018712626?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>肯德基和成都杜甫草堂博物馆合作打造了一家天府锦绣主题餐厅。</strong></a>顾客可以在店内欣赏杜甫草堂的名家作品。此外，肯德基推出了联名套餐，里面包括了文创周边。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307131142ILVKYclRnZWxMOQy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.672183\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307131142v07bfcQpLGZMwlgu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307131143kPnwjBhlFZy38zuU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307131143CHRGXNkdWzcSEBhw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307131143Hbl5GUa7W9cFO0ED.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307131144cl6QxwGMvYpTjgC0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307131207Uwl5QciS4kW3y1Yt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307131143TM7QNRe2s9hUJGDi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>星巴克推出女神月定制星意卡卡面活动。</strong>用户进入星巴克用星说小程序，选择品牌提供的背景和元素，生成自己设计的卡面。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307131228YnAUwGu6M7P3V4QE.png\" data-ratio=\"1.341912\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307131228LPJDQHAp0IEWlj6z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.721980\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://adage.com/article/cmo-strategy/mcdonald-s-success-waze-boosting-ad-results-marketer-s/316886/?utm_source=CMO%20Strategy&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed:+AdvertisingAge/CMO%20Strategy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">麦当劳和导航应用 Waze 合作推出户外广告。</a>300 个广告牌分布在加尼福利亚州南部，当 Waze 用户停止驾驶至少四秒钟时，手机应用上就会出现一个和附近广告牌相匹配的手机广告。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307131252muDePvShJ37qlWwk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BurGyoZA3rc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Buzzfeed 制作了一份报纸在美国街头发放。</strong></a>这份 12 页的报纸选择了互联网上热议的内容，头版是关于 Momo 挑战赛的故事，还把奥斯卡上 Glenn Close 检查礼服的 Gif 拆开呈现。不过它目前就做这一次。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307131307RG5QJPv2zZeonki1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.561798\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307131307sKYWuZJEndrafPLl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.345000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307131307aKSyohkj5IpHEDAO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.561798\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903071313085jKX46cyJiFDaenQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.561798\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Vans 推出 “This Is Off The Wall” 品牌活动。<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gNxLkYUNkSM\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>第一个广告 <em>Vanguards</em> 聚焦在来自不同国家的女子滑板运动员和她们各自的滑板风格，</strong></a>3 月 8 日还将举行一系列滑板研讨会。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=p0846qerccu\"></iframe> </figure> </div><h3>其他，也很重要</h3><p><a href=\"https://adage.com/article/digital/instagram-lets-brands-promote-influencer-posts-ad/316869/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Instagram 正在开发一种新的广告投放方式 “Branded content ads” （品牌内容广告）。</strong></a>广告主未来找 KOL 推广产品，只触达到 KOL 的粉丝，以此来强化内容传播效果。这意味着，投放方式将会进行更精准的监测，如果 KOL 有假粉丝和假数据，可能无法和品牌进行合作了。</p><p><a href=\"https://adage.com/article/digital/google-adx-moving-a-price-auction/316894/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Google 正在调整 Adx 的竞价规则，从原来的第二价格拍卖变为第一价格拍卖（first-price auction）。</strong></a>之前广告主支付的是投标者中第二高的价格，新规则之后，广告主不知道其他人的价格，可能在短期内为广告支付更多的费用，直到调整好品牌战略。这将会影响到 480 亿的市场环境。</p><p>题图来自：&nbsp;<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/HqYWQo7l49w?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\" rel=\"nofollow\">Maxime Lebrun</a> on <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/search/photos/kfc-store?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\" rel=\"nofollow\">Unsplash</a></p>"}